item.title: Eimear Walshe - Romantic Ireland (Venice Biennale 2024)
item.description: Venice Biennale Multimedia Installation Production Team, Technical Consultant, File Management/Archivist Eimear Walshe’s multimodal piece ‘Romantic Ireland’ was produced to represent Ireland at the 2024 Venice Biennale Arte. I worked as part of the project’s production team, as a shoot assistant for a test shoot, as well as file management/archivist for the project’s video shoots.
